    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-80ad-bc74-d42ce3ea3535",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors show this approach to outperform both BKT and DKT with minimal parameter tuning, with the advantage of mantaining the BKT interpretability that comes with probability estimates of skill, student mastery and question correctedness. \n\n\n",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-80ad-bc74-d42ce3ea3535",
